<div class="nbunit" id="3Feb1933"><font color="red">3 February 1933</font> <i>GILLET</i> (memoir): Last year, of course, nothing could be done. When one lives in such anxiety and such distress &hellip; it&apos;s easy to say: shut yourself up and work. But when your art and your life are one, when they are interwoven in the same fabric, as in my case, there you are </div>
